Milton St., St Paul, MN 55104', '- Apartments run from front to back along one side of the building;', '- 1st or 2nd floor unit available', '- Flexible move in (July, August, Sept 1)', '- Rent $1,345/mo + Utilities  (Electric + Natural Gas (heat and stove) will run approx $150/mo combined)', '- Required Lease Term: Through 6/30/23', '- Smoke-Free!!', 'All leases prohibit smoking, candles, and incense anywhere inside the building or on the property outside.', '- 2-BR, LR/DR, Kitchen, Bath', '- The approximate total size of the apartment is 900 sq ft', '- Great sunny front BR or a wonderful office!', '- The quoted rent is for 2 PEOPLE.', ' If there is a 3rd person, there is an additional $75/mo rent.', ' Maximum of 3 residents on the lease.', 'Location:', '- Two blocks north of Summit Ave (three blocks north of Grand Ave)', '- 1-block west of Victoria St', '- You are close to the many shops and scenic areas St. Paul has to offer.', '- For law students, we are 1-block north of the Mitchell Hamline College of Law.', ' #GreatForMitchellStudents #GreatForMitchellHamlineStudents', 'Our apartments feature:', '- Hardwood floors', '- Laundry and large private Storage Room in basement common area', '- Off-street parking (space is limited)', '- Sorry, no pet dogs', '** We are a family run business, not a big management company, who really cares for our buildings and the tenants so you will receive personal attention and care if you choose to rent from us.', 'For more information and details on the specific apartments, please contact the property managers directly and reference this CL ad:', 'Alisa or Brenna', 'Day:', 'show contact info', 'Evening:', 'show contact info', 'Email:  see craigslist "reply to" link at top of this ad', 'Website for more information:', 'http://www.apts.cc', 'This 2BR APARTMENT is for rent at 93 North Milton Street, Saint Paul, MN 55104 and 99 North Milton Street, Saint Paul, MN 55104']
